==生平==
戈文达是印度[[宝莱坞|宝莱坞]]的知名演员。1986年出道，参演《{{link-en|Ilzaam|Ilzaam}}》。此后到2010年代初已参演超过165部[[印度电影|印度电影]]。<ref name=five>{{cite web |title=Govinda: David Dhawan and I have not spoken in five years |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Govinda-David-Dhawan-and-I-have-not-spoken-in-five-years/articleshow/42238356.cms |access-date=2015-05-02 |archive-date=2020-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107153734/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Govinda-David-Dhawan-and-I-have-not-spoken-in-five-years/articleshow/42238356.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>1980年代，他演的电影种类很多，家庭片、剧情片、动作片、爱情片都有。1990年代，逐渐成为喜剧片演员。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.mid-day.com/entertainment/2012/mar/250312-Directors-double-dilemma.htm | title=Directors double dilemma | date=1 July 1999 | accessdate=25 March 2010 | archive-date=2013-12-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203064304/http://www.mid-day.com/entertainment/2012/mar/250312-Directors-double-dilemma.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>他曾12次获得[[印度电影观众奖|印度电影观众奖]]提名，获得一次印度电影观众特别奖（{{link-en|Filmfare Special Award|Filmfare Special Award}}）及一次印度电影观众奖最佳喜剧演员奖（{{link-en|Filmfare Award for Best Comedian|Filmfare Award for Best Performance in a Comic Role}}），还获得4次Zee电影奖（{{link-en|Zee Cine Awards|Zee Cine Awards}}）。他还曾经从政，是[[印度国大党|印度国大党]]党员，曾任第14届印度[[人民院_(印度)|人民院]]议员。<ref name=five/>

